data.description: Welcome to your dream home on a quiet cul-de-sac in Granger Pines! This beautiful home has everything you need for comfortable living. The spacious and inviting living area boasts high ceilings and plenty of natural light pouring in through the large windows. The kitchen is perfect for hosting gatherings, with stainless steel appliances and a large island for additional prep space. The kitchen leads to the dining area and a cozy den, perfect for relaxing after a long day. Escape to the primary suite, complete with an en-suite bathroom, double sinks, and a large walk-in shower. Upstairs, the game room offers a fantastic opportunity for indoor entertainment and fun. Walk outside and enjoy the covered patio and large yard! Enjoy the serene outdoor space in the backyard, which is ideal for gatherings and enjoying the fresh air. Other features of this charming home include a laundry room and a two-car garage. ABSOLUTELY NO “SUBJECT TO” OR CREATIVE OFFERS WILL BE CONSIDERED.
